PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FA quarter of the sandwiches (25%) are
OL,7,Fclassified as "less healthy" under the
OL,8,Fcurrent 2004/5 Nutrient Profiling
OL,9,FModel, limiting how and where they can
OL,10,Fbe promoted to shoppers.
OL,12,FThe research found that sandwiches
OL,13,Fbought out-of-home (OOH) were
OL,14,Fgenerally saltier than those sold in
OL,15,Fsupermarkets.
OL,17,FAmong the poorest performers with
OL,18,Fnaturally salty or heavily processed
OL,19,Fingredients were:
