OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FAll contain more salt than 12 standard
OL,7,Fbags of ready salted crisps.
OL,9,FHowever, Action on Salt & Sugar found
OL,10,Fwide differences in the salt content
OL,11,Fof similar sandwiches and fillings,
OL,12,Fsuch as Pret A Manger's Chicken Salad
OL,13,FSandwich containing 2.22g of salt, vs
OL,14,FGreggs' Roast Chicken Salad Sandwich
OL,15,Fcontaining half as much again with
OL,16,F1.1g of salt.
OL,18,FSimilarly, an M&S All Day Breakfast
OL,19,FSandwich contained 2.65g of salt,
OL,20,Fcompared with 1.54g in Sainsbury's All
OL,21,FDay Breakfast Sandwich.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
