CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FThe study also says that several lower-
OL,7,Fsalt products showed that
OL,8,Freformulation was "both possible and
OL,9,Fpractical", including:
OL,11,FThere were also "clear examples of
OL,12,Fcompanies getting it right", including
OL,13,Fevery product surveyed from Pollen +
OL,14,FGrace, The Gym Kitchen, and Urban
OL,15,FRajah, which all met calorie and salt
OL,16,Freduction targets, had no red warning
OL,17,Flabels on front of pack, and none of
OL,18,Ftheir sandwiches was classed as high
OL,19,Fin fat, sugar or salt (HFSS).
