CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FAmong retailers, Asda and Lidl
OL,7,Fachieved full compliance with the salt
OL,8,Ftargets for sandwiches, and Starbucks
OL,9,Fand Greggs provided the lowest average
OL,10,Fsalt levels in the OOH sector, with
OL,11,Ffull compliance with the salt and
OL,12,Fcalorie targets.
