PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FStudies suggest that UK adults consume
OL,7,F8.4g of salt a day on average, 40%
OL,8,Fabove the maximum limit, with much of
OL,9,Fit hidden in processed, pre-packed and
OL,10,Fout-of-home foods such as sandwiches.
OL,12,FToo much salt raises blood pressure, a
OL,13,Fleading cause of stroke and a major
OL,14,Fdriver of heart and kidney disease.
OL,16,FConsumers buy 11.5 billion sandwiches
OL,17,Facross the UK every year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
