PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,FSonia Pombo, head of research and
OL,7,Fimpact at Action on Salt & Sugar,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Most people choose sandwiches
OL,9,Ffor lunch for their simplicity,
OL,10,Fconvenience and affordability. But
OL,11,Fwhat they're actually eating can be a
OL,12,Ffull day's worth of salt hidden
OL,13,Fbetween two slices of bread.
OL,15,F"More than 20 years after the first
OL,16,Fset of salt reduction targets were
OL,17,Fintroduced, it's frankly unacceptable
OL,18,Fthat some companies continue to sell
OL,19,Fsandwiches that exceed an adult's
OL,20,Fdaily limit in one go.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
