PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778637819
OL,3,C'Alarmingly high' levels of salt found
OL,4,Cin some of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,6,F"Voluntary action has been allowed to
OL,7,Fdrift for too long, and the result is
OL,8,Fa food environment that continues to
OL,9,Fput public health at risk. The
OL,10,FGovernment must now step in with
OL,11,Ftough, mandatory measures, because
OL,12,Fleaving this to industry goodwill has
OL,13,Fclearly failed."
